<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="cat-page-faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cat-page-faq-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Frequently asked</span>
      <h2>What people ask us most about advanced facials.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-page-faq-list">
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item open">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">How do I know if I need a peel or dermapen? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>It depends on the issue. Pigmentation and sun damage respond better to depigmenting chemical peels; scars, fine lines and uneven texture respond better to dermapen. In the free assessment we'll tell you exactly what your skin needs.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">How much downtime will I need? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>It depends on the treatment. Dermaplaning and virtual mesotherapy: zero. Hydration with dermapen and gentle peels: 24–48h with mild redness. Deep chemical peels: 4–7 days of controlled flaking. We'll explain it in detail before choosing your protocol.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">When will I see results? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>Treatments such as a collagen veil or dermaplaning give instant glow from the very first session. Anti-pigmentation peels and dermapen for scars are progressive: you'll notice improvement within a month and full results across 3–5 sessions depending on the case.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">Can I combine several treatments? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>Yes, and it's often the best strategy. Dermapen + hydration, peel + radiofrequency, mesotherapy + collagen veil are common combinations. In your bespoke plan we'll design the optimal sequence.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">I have sensitive skin / rosacea / I'm pregnant. Are there alternatives? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>Yes. We have specific protocols for sensitive and reactive skin. If you're pregnant or breastfeeding, some treatments are contraindicated but others are perfectly safe — we'll tell you straight in the assessment with clinical honesty.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

